<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EcoVolt Learning Center - Paid Courses</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/learningCentre.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <!-- <img src="images/ecovolt-logo.png" alt="EcoVolt Logo" class="logo" /> -->
      <nav><%- include("_nav.ejs") %></nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>
          Empower Yourself. Master Renewable Energy with Our Paid Courses.
        </h1>
        <p>
          Gain the knowledge and skills to contribute to a sustainable future.
          Browse our comprehensive course library and unlock the power of
          renewable energy.
        </p>
        <a href="#courses" class="cta-button">Explore Courses</a>
      </section>

      <section class="course-categories" id="courses">
        <h2>Course Categories</h2>
        <div class="category-grid">
          <div class="category-card">
            <h3>Renewable Energy Fundamentals</h3>
            <p>
              Build a strong foundation in various renewable energy sources.
            </p>
            <a href="#renewablenergyfundamentals">View Courses</a>
          </div>
          <div class="category-card">
            <h3>Renewable Energy Applications</h3>
            <p>
              Learn how to implement renewable energy solutions in different
              settings.
            </p>
            <a href="#">View Courses</a>
          </div>
          <div class="category-card">
            <h3>Advanced Topics</h3>
            <p>Deep dive into specific technologies and industry trends.</p>
            <a href="#">View Courses</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="fundamentals" id="renewablenergyfundamentals">
        <h2>Renewable Energy Fundamentals</h2>

        <div class="course-grid">
          <div class="course-card">
            <h3>Introduction to Solar Energy</h3>
            <p class="course-price">FREE</p>
            <p class="course-description">
              Learn the fundamentals of solar power technology, including solar
              panel types, system components, and applications for homes and
              businesses.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="enroll-button">Enroll Now</a>
          </div>
          <div class="course-card">
            <h3>Understanding Wind Power</h3>
            <p class="course-price">ksh1,500</p>
            <p class="course-description">
              Explore the principles of wind energy generation, turbine
              technology, and how wind farms contribute to a sustainable energy
              mix.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="enroll-button">Enroll Now</a>
          </div>
          <div class="course-card">
            <h3>Hydropower: Generating Electricity from Water</h3>
            <p class="course-price">ksh5,000</p>
            <p class="course-description">
              Dive into hydropower technology, including different dam types,
              power generation processes, and the environmental considerations
              of hydropower.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="enroll-button">Enroll Now</a>
          </div>
          <div class="course-card">
            <h3>Geothermal Energy: Harnessing the Earth's Heat</h3>
            <p class="course-price">ksh3000</p>
            <p class="course-description">
              Understand the concept of geothermal energy, explore its
              applications for electricity generation and heating, and learn
              about its potential for sustainable development.
            </p>
            <a href="#" href="#" class="enroll-button">Enroll Now</a>
          </div>
          <div class="course-card">
            <h3>Biomass Energy: Power from Organic Materials</h3>
            <p class="course-price">ksh4000</p>
            <p class="course-description">
              Discover the various ways biomass can be used for energy
              production, including biofuels, biogas, and the sustainability
              considerations of biomass energy.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="enroll-button">Enroll Now</a>
          </div>
          <div class="course-card">
            <h3>Introduction to Battery Storage for Renewables</h3>
            <p class="course-price">ksh 2,500</p>
            <p class="course-description">
              Learn about the importance of battery storage for integrating
              renewable energy sources into the grid, explore different battery
              technologies, and understand their role in a sustainable energy
              future.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="enroll-button">Enroll Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
